                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.512/911.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Parker</persName>, representing
                        American interests in Mexico, to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico City</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-11-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 22, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>161. My 59, September 8. Department of Finance published yesterday an
                    authorization to governors of states to collect the proportionable tax on mines
                    corresponding to each state on Mexican gold basis, which implies a further
                    increase on the recently augmented tax.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Parker.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
